    "causal_summary": "The sk-design `manualtestingplaybook` has never been exercised end-to-end against the real `cli-opencode` orchestrator for two specific behavioral guarantees: that `harden` and `polish` are excluded from `audit` transform-verb aliasing (`TV-005`), and that the four non-md-generator design modes correctly use `backendKind: reference-base` while the shared reference base itself is never invoked as a user-facing workflow (`SR-002`, `SR-003`)",
